eth_prices_df = eth.history(period='max', interval='1d')[['Close']]

crypto_df.fillna(method='ffill', inplace=True)
crypto_returns_df = 100 * (crypto_df.loc['2018-01-01':].pct_change()+1).cumprod()
crypto_returns_df.sample(20)
